title: Baker Mayfield calls out Daniel Jones and Fantasy Draft Strategies with Adam Aizer (Football 8/21)
description:
Fantasy Week continues as Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner-McGough and the host of the 'Fantasy Football Today' podcast, Adam Aizer. The guys react to the Cowboys handing out an extension not to Dak, Zeke or Amari, but Jaylon Smith. Plus your daily Antonio Brown update and some continuing drama between the Browns and Giants. Then, Adam dishes out his draft strategies for different league styles and sizes.
